name: R5-care-plan-intent-for-R4B
title: Cross-version VS for R5.CarePlanIntent for use in FHIR R4B
description: This cross-version ValueSet represents concepts from http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/care-plan-intent|5.0.0 for use in FHIR R4B. Concepts not present here have direct `equivalent` mappings crossing all versions from R5 to R4B.
